  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Spac Review",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Copyright 1953 by ALBERT K. BENDER",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "VOL II, No. 1",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "January, 1953",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Bridgeport, Conn., U.S.A.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "IFSB OF BRITAIN ORGANIZES",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Capt. E. L. Plunkett Appointed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "British Representative",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "The IFSB has finally been organized in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Great Britain with retired Capt. E. L. Plun-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "kett of the 8th Army as British Represen-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "tative. Mr. Plunkett resides at 71 Ched-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "worth Rd., Horfield, Bristol 7, England.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Denis, son of Mr. Plunkett, is the assistant",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "representative, but is now serving his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "country in the Royal Air Force.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Rep. Plunkett has shown great interest",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "and foresight in forming the IFSB in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "British Isles. Numerous articles have ap-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "peared in leading newspapers through his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "efforts. He is planning on using local halls",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "and auditoriums to give lectures and show",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "pictures with the aid of an ediascope.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "He also plans to give talks at the local",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Y.M.C.A. of the city which is a semi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "war veterans type of society.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Many people in the British Isles have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "contacted Mr. Plunkett showing great in-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "terest in IFSB. Most of these people are",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "very learned individuals such as officers in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "the Armed Forces, members of the British",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Inter-Planetary Society, Aero-Dynamists,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "newspaper reporters, and flying saucer en-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "thusiasts.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "At present Mr. Plunkett is holding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "weekly meetings at his home, where they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "discuss IFSB and flying saucers in general.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "For further information about our Brit-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "ish Representative see page twelve of this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "issue.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "LUIS LUHRING NAMED",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "PUERTO RICAN REPRESENTATIVE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Mr. Luis Luhring of Punta Santiago,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Puerto Rico, has accepted the position of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Representative for the island of Puerto",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "Rico. He will handle all IFSB business in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "that place. Write to Box 23, Punta Santi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "ago, Puerto Rico. Mr. Luhring is a very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "capable man and will aid the IFSB greatly.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "FRANKLIN, INDIANA JOINS EN MASSE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "Business Men and Public Officials Join",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "IFSB To Form Own City Group.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "The City of Franklin, Indiana, has gone",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "out fully for the IFSB and is now the only",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "city in the world that has the most mem-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "bers in our organization. Through the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "great efforts and work of Mr. Louis Frahm,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "business man; Mr. Jack W. Moore, police-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "man; Mr. Robert Wolf, civilian defense",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "director, and Mr. Dick Campbell, IFSB",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "Representative for Indiana, this great ac-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "complishment was made possible. At this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "publication, Franklin can claim 20 mem-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "bers with ten from nearly towns, giving",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "a total of 30. Since all this interest has been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "aroused Mr. Frahm plans to form a city",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "group with their own chairman, secretary",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "and treasurer. Among the members you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "will find policemen, librarians, mechanics,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "commercial pilots, business men, bus driv-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "ers, students, etc. The group plans to pur-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "chase a telescope of suitable power. In ad-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "dition to this they plan to rig up a 3 1/4 x",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "4 1/4 Graflex camera with an optical type",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "view finder and a reen door handle on each",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "side for easy handling. This is the equip-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "ment they plan to start with. Later, if fi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "nances permit, they may build a portable",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "radar set.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "Franklin, Indiana, and nearby towns,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "have been fortunate in having had at least",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "four sightings this past summer. Two were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "witnessed by Mr. Frahm and Mr. Moore.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "Reports of these sightings are reviewed in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "this issue of Space Review.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "OUR PRESIDENT HEARS FROM",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "PROF. EINSTEIN",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "Mr. Al K. Bender, President of IFSB,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "received a letter from Professor Einstein",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "with this message: \"Having no experience",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "and only superficial knowledge in the field",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "I regret not to be able to comply with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "your request.\" Mr. Bender wanted his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "opinion on the flying saucers. This was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "the Professor's reply.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "62-83894-326",
      "status": "image_matched"
    }
  ],
  "blockCount": null
}
